______________________________________________________<br>
Some new wizard spells are currently on the Test Server.  An extension of the translocate series, should these spells go live they would enable Wizards to send players one at a time to certain Wizard spires throughout the world of Norrath, without having to zone themselves.  As always with test information, these spells could change before going live, or not go live at all.<br>
<br>
Translocate: Combine <br>
Translocate: Fay <br>
Translocate: North <br>
Translocate: Tox <br>
______________________________________________________<br>
<br>
While I definitely think there is a place for these spells, it doesn't answer one of the 50+ wizards major complaints: what is being done to make the wizard class more attractive to groups so that I can walk in to a dungeon, /ooc 52 wiz lfg, and get a response. These enhancements just mean that I have to go /role to keep from getting spammed with requests for ports.<br>
<br>
Hmmm, these are not the fixes I've been looking for.<br>
Verant Employee: These are not the fixes you're looking for.<br>
<br>
Spora<br>
52 Channeller - Saryrn<br>
Towers of Elysium<br>
